Herbert Heywood (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbert_Heywood_(actor) 0 Herbert Heywood (February 1, 1881 – September 15, 1964) was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 120 films between 1915 and 1950. Herbert_Heywood ( February_1_,_1881 – September_15_,_1964 ) was an_American_film_actor .
